Title: KitchenAid® 10 Inch Skillet Hard-Anodized, with Nonstick
Description: The KitchenAid® 10” Hard Anodized, Non-Stick Skillet is a great addition to your kitchen for all your cooking creations. Heavy gauge hard-anodized construction is twice as strong as stainless steel and distributes heat evenly. A long lasting, 3-layer non-stick interior ensures your food will slide effortlessly out of the pan and makes clean up a snap. The double riveted, silicone and stainless steel comfortable handle offers exceptional quality and comfort when in use.
